  <li><a href="https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2010SPIE.7735E..2KL/abstract">Lee+ 2010</a>: <em>GMTNIRS (Giant Magellan Telescope near-infrared spectrograph): design concept</em></li>
