<h1>The Raw &amp; Reduced IGRINS Spectral Archive (RRISA)</h1>
<p>As of May 2021, IGRINS has completed almost 12,000 individual observations of both science targets and telluric standards.
RRISA features IGRINS data from more than 850 nights on-sky, resulting in 2,800 unique target observations from over 3,000 hours of total science time.
RRISA also includes IGRINS observations of over 1,200 distinct A0V standard stars.</p>

